Milestone 1: Environment Setup & Initial Training (Weeks 1-2)
Objectives:
Set up the project environment (Maven, Java, MySQL)
Define data models (Account, Transaction)
Basic JDBC configuration

Steps:
Create Maven Project Structure
Create the directory structure as shown above.
Create pom.xml with necessary dependencies (MySQL Connector, JUnit, Jakarta Mail).
Define Data Models
Implement Account class (src/main/java/com/banking/model/Account.java)
Implement Transaction class (src/main/java/com/banking/model/Transaction.java)
Set Up Database
Create MySQL database and tables (sql/database_setup.sql)
Implement DatabaseManager class (src/main/java/com/banking/database/DatabaseManager.java) for basic JDBC operations.

Configuration:
Create BankingConfig class (src/main/java/com/banking/config/BankingConfig.java)
and configuration file (src/main/resources/banking_config.properties).
